Comment: 10,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Comment: 10,0:08:27.43,0:08:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And now to break the seal.
Comment: 10,0:09:41.02,0:09:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this?
Comment: 10,0:09:54.71,0:09:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, all citizens involved in the riot!
Comment: 10,0:09:58.02,0:10:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You are to disperse immediately!
Comment: 10,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Failure to comply will result in—
Comment: 10,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A coup d'état?!{## really nice match cut}
Comment: 10,0:10:04.40,0:10:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, it's only a rumor.
Comment: 10,0:10:07.05,0:10:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,However, going by the videos of the riots that have been put online, a coup d'état is a real possibility.
Comment: 10,0:10:12.62,0:10:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable. Do the people in that country have no sense at all? {implied that the coup is in the 'other' country}{## hard to imply this... maybe "Does that nation"}
Comment: 10,0:10:15.79,0:10:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather more detailed intelligence.{## information that is more detailed, or more of the detailed information? maybe just "intelligence"? "Gather more intelligence" sounds like a bad zinger though. "See to gathering more intelligence" maybe.}{you see, I considered 'intelligence', but isn't that a government term? oh, wait...}
Comment: 10,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A coup d'état, huh...
Comment: 10,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We may be able to use this.
Comment: 10,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Use" how so?{## "howso" is super rare and not used like this anyway}
Comment: 10,0:10:23.34,0:10:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Our moderates are far too soft on that nation.
Comment: 10,0:10:26.80,0:10:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But faced with a coup d'état, those pacifists\Nwill have no choice but to open their eyes.{## was briefly considering "peaceniks" but it looked weird and out of place on-screen}
Comment: 10,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Deploying the military might be imperative.
Comment: 10,0:10:33.72,0:10:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You intend to exploit another country's crisis?!
Comment: 10,0:10:37.08,0:10:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Andrew!
Comment: 10,0:10:39.22,0:10:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and gather more intelligence.{## or intelligence depending on edit above}
Comment: 10,0:10:47.66,0:10:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Change the world! {all undone because it barely nicked the eyecatch}
Comment: 10,0:10:53.83,0:10:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 10,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all wrong!
Comment: 10,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be true!
Comment: 10,0:10:57.63,0:11:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way {\fax-0.2}this{\i0} is the world reconstruction magic!
Comment: 10,0:11:03.48,0:11:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wrong!
Comment: 10,0:11:10.23,0:11:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way... {\fax-0.2}this{\i0} is the Grand Triskelion...
Comment: 10,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This banal...
Comment: 10,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Croix...
Comment: 10,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Woodward!
Comment: 10,0:11:28.92,0:11:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the Grand Triskelion?
Comment: 10,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?!
Comment: 10,0:11:34.55,0:11:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You already hold it in your hands.
Comment: 10,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie!
Comment: 10,0:11:39.14,0:11:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It is the truth.
Comment: 10,0:11:40.67,0:11:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why isn't anything happening?!
Comment: 10,0:11:43.30,0:11:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What part of this do you call world reconstruction magic?!
Comment: 10,0:11:46.26,0:11:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you always look right past me?
Comment: 10,0:11:49.90,0:11:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you guide me?
Comment: 10,0:11:52.88,0:11:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you'll never choose me...
Comment: 10,0:11:55.40,0:11:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then stop showing me your face!
Comment: 10,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Comment: 10,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Croix!
Comment: 10,0:12:12.76,0:12:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotional Pattern:
Comment: 10,0:12:14.57,0:12:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Red. Red. Red. Red.
Comment: 10,0:12:18.24,0:12:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,R-R-R-RRRRR—
Comment: 10,0:12:20.03,0:12:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Comment: 10,0:12:29.78,0:12:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Comment: 10,0:12:31.99,0:12:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Comment: 10,0:12:32.69,0:12:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn off the machine!
Comment: 10,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... it's not stopping!
Comment: 10,0:13:04.59,0:13:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even {\fax-0.2}you{\i0} betray me in the end?!
Comment: 10,0:13:23.12,0:13:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?
Comment: 10,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What...
Comment: 10,0:14:03.01,0:14:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Comment: 10,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Croix!
Comment: 10,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Chariot!
Comment: 10,0:14:20.85,0:14:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Chariot!
Comment: 10,0:14:22.83,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Comment: 10,0:14:25.87,0:14:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's after me.
Comment: 10,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me and go!
Comment: 10,0:14:29.48,0:14:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 10,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll never abandon you!
Comment: 10,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll both be—
Comment: 10,0:14:43.29,0:14:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get Croix!{## anything better for "get"?}{well, I mean, she doesn't say "kill" directly}
Comment: 10,0:14:45.63,0:14:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Chariot...
Comment: 10,0:14:48.98,0:14:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Chariot...
Comment: 10,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done enough!
Comment: 10,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't!
Comment: 10,0:14:54.33,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I stole your dream!
Comment: 10,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I stole Akko's power!
Comment: 10,0:14:58.62,0:15:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I won't let anything more be stolen! {first, the an8 was eh. second, I feel the "anything" is important}
Comment: 10,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Chariot...
Comment: 10,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Chariot!
Comment: 10,0:15:10.21,0:15:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Murowa!{## ep2}
Comment: 10,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Comment: 10,0:15:17.40,0:15:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko!
Comment: 10,0:15:19.49,0:15:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding...
Comment: 10,0:15:20.72,0:15:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This one looks pretty dangerous.
Comment: 10,0:15:22.80,0:15:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? We're all still in danger.
Comment: 10,0:15:33.99,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Its energy link is starting to break.
Comment: 10,0:15:37.91,0:15:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Comment: 10,0:15:41.21,0:15:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Comment: 10,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Croix!
Comment: 10,0:15:47.75,0:15:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Comment: 10,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}The Words!{## ep1 1937}
Comment: 10,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Cast the spell!
Comment: 10,0:16:01.68,0:16:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,725)\fax-0.2}Noctu Orfei! {forget this one in editing?}
Comment: 10,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Noctu... Orfei!
Comment: 10,0:16:06.15,0:16:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Aude!
Comment: 10,0:16:08.33,0:16:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Aude!
Comment: 10,0:16:11.01,0:16:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraetor!
Comment: 10,0:16:15.63,0:16:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiny Arc!
Comment: 10,0:16:55.91,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it... you did it, Akko!
Comment: 10,0:17:14.94,0:17:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko...
Comment: 10,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Chariot...
Comment: 10,0:17:19.52,0:17:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We finally meet!
Comment: 10,0:17:22.84,0:17:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Comment: 10,0:17:24.89,0:17:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 10,0:17:27.09,0:17:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't mine.
Comment: 10,0:17:28.43,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I made up my mind to return it\Nto Chariot once I found her.
Comment: 10,0:17:32.60,0:17:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept it!
Comment: 10,0:17:35.42,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw one of your Chariot shows when I was a child.
Comment: 10,0:17:38.78,0:17:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so pretty and fun and cool,\Nand it felt like I was in a dream!
Comment: 10,0:17:42.86,0:17:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even describe how moved I was!
Comment: 10,0:17:45.07,0:17:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when I decided to become a witch.
Comment: 10,0:17:48.25,0:17:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I believed that if I became a witch,\NI'd be able to see Chariot again.
Comment: 10,0:17:52.78,0:17:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That was my dream!
Comment: 10,0:17:55.94,0:17:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I've met you.
Comment: 10,0:17:59.23,0:18:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream... came true.
Comment: 10,0:18:03.60,0:18:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko...
Comment: 10,0:18:05.56,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But this only happened thanks to everyone.
Comment: 10,0:18:09.38,0:18:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We met at school, got to know each other, and became friends.
Comment: 10,0:18:14.48,0:18:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I caused them lots of trouble and was always getting helped, and that's what brought me here. {that completely changes the meaning}
Comment: 10,0:18:20.24,0:18:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Without them, I never would've made it.
Comment: 10,0:18:25.65,0:18:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to them, and... and also...
Comment: 10,0:18:29.12,0:18:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you.
Comment: 10,0:18:35.30,0:18:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, it still doesn't feel real\Nthat you're actually Chariot.
Comment: 10,0:18:40.32,0:18:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because to me, you're my teacher.
Comment: 10,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Comment: 10,0:18:45.47,0:18:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you please keep being my Professor Ursula?
Comment: 10,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko...
Comment: 10,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who took your—
Comment: 10,0:18:54.63,0:18:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Comment: 10,0:18:55.93,0:18:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand now.
Comment: 10,0:18:57.96,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never be Chariot.
Comment: 10,0:19:02.20,0:19:08.85,Default,,13,13,0,,I wanted to be like Chariot, gracefully soaring through the sky and using beautiful transformation magic.
Comment: 10,0:19:09.51,0:19:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But Chariot is Chariot, and I'm me.{## holy shit mouthflap any which way i look}{rekt}
Comment: 10,0:19:13.37,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only be myself.
Comment: 10,0:19:16.00,0:19:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I can't fly and always mess up.
Comment: 10,0:19:19.37,0:19:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko...
Comment: 10,0:19:20.97,0:19:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, I'll keep working even harder!
Comment: 10,0:19:24.77,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work hard to become a witch\Nwho can make everyone smile.
Comment: 10,0:19:28.23,0:19:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Because to me, magic is the most wonderful thing in the entire world!
Comment: 10,0:19:32.35,0:19:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So please keep on teaching me how to use magic, just like you always have!{## i just can't cover that beautiful smile}{hey guess what, I can. because eyes are far more important than the mouth. they're the gateway to our souls}
Comment: 10,0:19:43.65,0:19:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're fine with me?
Comment: 10,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want anybody else. {interestingly, that が adds some important emotional information}
Comment: 10,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you, Professor.
Comment: 10,0:19:55.57,0:19:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I love you.
Comment: 10,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Akko.
Comment: 10,0:19:59.79,0:20:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You made my dream come true.
Comment: 10,0:20:10.19,0:20:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Comment: 10,0:20:13.36,0:20:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko.
Comment: 10,0:20:17.36,0:20:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your feelings into words.
Comment: 10,0:20:21.32,0:20:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They will surely be the final Word.
Comment: 10,0:20:35.13,0:20:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Change the world.
Comment: 10,0:20:37.40,0:20:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Connect with other people, and your dreams will grow.
Comment: 10,0:20:41.91,0:20:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Phasansheer Shearylla!
Comment: 10,0:20:54.14,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Comment: 10,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it just a stick?
Comment: 10,0:20:57.43,0:21:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the world reconstruction magic? Diana...
Comment: 10,0:21:00.68,0:21:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, I'm afraid I'm not sure...
Comment: 10,0:21:04.55,0:21:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Try it out and see what happens.{## such irresponsible words, you can't just go and casually reconstruct the world dude}
Comment: 10,0:21:08.58,0:21:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 10,0:21:13.54,0:21:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Phasansheer Shearylla!
Comment: 10,0:21:47.07,0:21:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This... is the world reconstruction magic?
